        <p data-role="text">Changi Air&#xAD;port is rolling out a slew of at&#xAD;trac&#xAD;tions to cre&#xAD;ate a year-end fes&#xAD;tive cheer, with an eye on eval&#xAD;u&#xAD;at&#xAD;ing whether the new prod&#xAD;ucts can be a big draw for in&#xAD;com&#xAD;ing vis&#xAD;i&#xAD;tors when travel re&#xAD;cov&#xAD;ers. At Ter&#xAD;mi&#xAD;nal 3, the Juras&#xAD;sic era takes the spot&#xAD;light with di&#xAD;nosaur dis&#xAD;plays and ac&#xAD;tiv&#xAD;i&#xAD;ties for chil&#xAD;dren.</p>
